Package seng201.team53.game.items

Class Cart

java.lang.Object
seng201.team53.game.items.Cart
All Implemented Interfaces:
Upgradeable
public class Cart extends Object implements Upgradeable
Represents a cart. Each cart has a determined max capacity, velocity and resource type. The state of the cart is kept track of in this class along with the current capacity and velocity modifier.

  • Constructor Details

    • Cart

      public Cart(int maxCapacity, float velocity, ResourceType acceptedResource, javafx.util.Duration spawnDelayTime)
      Construct a new cart with the given parameters. A listener for the game state property will be added to wait for the game round to start, then after waiting for the spawnDelay time, set the cart to start traversing the path.
      Parameters:
      maxCapacity - The max capacity of the cart
      velocity - The velocity of the cart
      acceptedResource - The resource that the cart accepts
      spawnDelayTime - The delay time until the cart spawns and starts collecting resources
